This seed returns nodes generally, not only nodes from open-nodes.org itself?

Yes, not only nodes from open-node.org itself. It use [open-nodes/bitcoin-seeder](https://github.com/open-nodes/bitcoin-seeder) as seeds DNS server, which forked from [sipa/bitcoin-seeder](https://github.com/sipa/bitcoin-seeder). open-node.org just build only one hub node now(1000+ connections, still in test), we will setup 10+ bitcoin hub nodes in the future.
